00:11:09.993 --> 00:11:12.513
Tengo otra cosa que hacer.

00:11:12.873 --> 00:11:14.834
Bañarte sola.

00:11:17.873 --> 00:11:18.513
Lo vi.

00:11:21.034 --> 00:11:22.714
Tu rostro se puso rojo

00:11:27.034 --> 00:11:28.154
