00:14:20.193 --> 00:14:21.073
Ni siquiera nos vimos.

00:14:21.193 --> 00:14:21.954
Detente.

00:14:22.073 --> 00:14:22.914
No, déjame terminar.

00:14:23.834 --> 00:14:24.354
Xiaoliu,

00:14:25.234 --> 00:14:26.914
